# ── Meta-proprietary / patched binaries — DO NOT PUBLISH ─────────
# The patcher operates on Meta's stock VrShell.apk (which embeds libshell.so).
# Neither the stock nor the patched apk may be redistributed — build your own
# from your device's VrShell via scripts/build_and_deploy.sh.
*.apk
*.apk.idsig
*.idsig
dist/
**/libshell.so
**/base.apk

